      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 Coupe, finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This S54-powered icon features a factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.62 limited-slip differential. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains in peak mechanical health, with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement already completed. The chassis retains its original rigidity with pristine bushings and a flawlessly damped suspension. Every individual throttle body is synchronized perfectly, delivering the razor-sharp throttle response this chassis is legendary for. This is a concours-ready example with zero deferred maintenance, offering a pure, visceral driving experience.",
